                                <q xml:lang="gez">ገድለ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡  ዘ<placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">ቅዱስ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም።</placeName>
